# HTML parsing

- Use HtmlAgilityPack only; keep selectors in HtmlProcessor
- Listing: div.regularEntries table → tr rows, cells as text|href
- Detail: #job → table.dtable → 4th tr for description
- Dates: Georgian month names via Ext.GetDate / GetMonth
- Verify selectors against live jobs.ge HTML when changing layout logic
- Job id from link query string: id=
